    "section_accordions_VC7eEK": {
      "type": "section-accordions",
      "blocks": {
        "text_rDxAky": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What is Order Protection?",
            "text": "<p>OrderProtection.com covers your order for every major issue that can occur during<br\/>shipping. Your order will be protected against loss, damage, theft, wrong items,<br\/>defective items and missing items.<\/p><p><br\/>If something goes wrong during shipping, you can quickly <a href=\"https:\/\/claims.orderprotection.com\/submitClaim\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/claims.orderprotection.com\/submitClaim\">file a claim<\/a> in a few clicks.<\/p><p><br\/>You'll receive a refund or reshipment if your claim is approved. To protect your order, make sure Order Protection is toggled on in your cart.<\/p>"
          }
        },
        "text_gDXdi6": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How do I purchase Order Protection?",
            "text": "<p>In your cart, there is a toggle to turn Order Protection on or off. Turn on OrderProtection to purchase protection for your order! If you have protection turned on, you will see it appear as a line item during checkout.<\/p>"
          }
        },
        "text_9HBnTR": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How do I file a claim with Order Protection?",
            "text": "<p><a href=\"https:\/\/claims.orderprotection.com\/submitClaim\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/claims.orderprotection.com\/submitClaim\">Click here to file a claim.<\/a><\/p><p>Please note that you’ll only be able to file a claim if you purchased Order Protectionwhen placing your order.<\/p>"
          }
        },
        "text_nxnwyF": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How long does it take for my claim to get resolved?",
            "text": "<p>You’ll typically get a response within an hour, and most claims are resolved that same day. OrderProtection.com has 24\/7 support staff so you can expect responses and communication around the clock.<\/p>"
          }
        },
        "text_CVnC38": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "I didn’t add Order Protection to my order, but I need to make a claim.",
            "text": "<p>If you chose not to purchase Order Protection at checkout, and you have an issue with your order, you’ll need to contact us directly at<a href=\"mailto:hi@shopcherri.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"mailto:hi@shopcherri.com\"> hi@shopcherri.com.<\/a><\/p>"
          }
        },
        "text_Ka8eNW": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How long do I have to make a claim?",
            "text": "<p>You can submit a claim 30 - 45 days from the date you placed your order depending on the claim type.<\/p>"
          }
        },
        "text_tPyPVL": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What does Order Protection cover?",
            "text": "<p>OrderProtection.com covers your order for loss, damage, theft, wrong items, defective items and missing items.<\/p><p>If you need a different size, style, or color for an exchange, please email <a href=\"mailto:hi@shopcherri.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"mailto:hi@shopcherri.com\">hi@shopcherri.com<\/a>. Exchanges are always free, even if you don't have Order Protection.<\/p>"
          }
        },
        "text_hNVKBa": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How much does Order Protection cost?",
            "text": "<p>Order Protection can cost $0.98+ depending on the value of your order.<\/p>"
          }
        }
      },
